# Override monorepo root .gitignore: the motionbricks Python package uses
# `data/` and `models/` directory names for source code, not runtime
# artifacts. Re-include only the specific source directories.
!motionbricks/data/
!motionbricks/data/**
!motionbricks/motion_backbone/models/
!motionbricks/motion_backbone/models/**
!motionbricks/vqvae/models/
!motionbricks/vqvae/models/**
